RESOLUTION NO. 14-0398-2017

After due deliberation of the Sangguniang Panlungsod of the City of Lapu-Lapu, on motion of Hon. Nelson O. Yap duly seconded by Hon. Roque P. Wagwag and Hon. Eduardo R. Patalinjug,

RESOLVED, as it is hereby being resolved, to approve, as it is hereby being approved, the Application for Preliminary Approval/Locational Clearance and Development Permit of 77 Living spaces, Inc. for the proposed medium cost housing subdivision (Bali by Aldca Premier), located at barangay Agus, this City as per City Development Council Executive Committee Resolution No. 2016-07. PROVIDED, that the concerns of Honorable Gregorio A. Paquibot be addressed relative to the payment of all necessary taxes by the developer concerned and that the title will already be transferred in the name of the developer before the start of any actual development operation of the said project;

RESOLVED FURTHER, that copies of this resolution be furnished, the City Mayor, the City Planning and Development Coordinator and the applicant concerned, for their information and guidance.

CARRIED/APPROVED.

January 10, 2017

I hereby certify to the correctness of the above-quoted resolution.

FRANCISCO V. LIMPANGUG SP/City Secretary

ATTESTED:

MARCIAL A. YCONG Vice Mayor & Presiding Officer

APPROVED:

PAUL C. RADAZA City Mayor
